                </h3>
                <div class="author">
                    <a href="http://movie.douban.com/people/modestcat/">蘑菇精精</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;评论:&nbsp;<a href="http://movie.douban.com/subject/6753166/">Seven Psychopaths</a>
                </div>
                <p>百度一下Psychopaths:
精神变态者；变态人格者
A psychopath is someone who has serious mental problems and who may act in a violent way without feeling sorry for what they have done.

再百度一下精神变态：
精神变态是一种或者几种心理上的疾病总称，并不局限于我们日常生活中所说的意思。精神变态包括人...<a href="http://movie.douban.com/review/5730821/">(2回应)</a></p>
